{"tid":1300418,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狙擊TVB 之 流動連儂牆","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T14:30:47.000Z","uid":264873,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"751e39c1c2e2bfd6ab062538e977d98b7e5cdaf0","tid":1300418,"uid":264873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJoYAJC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJoYAJC.jpg&h=d395ea18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCCTVB長年累月場面製造假嘅、誤導嘅、偏頗嘅新聞已經到達令人髮指嘅地步，網絡上開始要諗辦法對付呢隻能入去千家萬戶嘅大怪獸。  呢個星期全港各區都出現一幅又一幅嘅連儂牆，大家從今日起，不妨隨身帶着五顏六色嘅post it同marker，去到邊貼到邊。  到底還有什麼地方可以貼？  突然間諗起幾年前台灣「反服貿運動」，有示威者因為不滿台灣傳媒報道偏頗，隨即將採訪車變成一幅流動連儂牆，將大家嘅心聲同不滿貼喺車上，以後出到街、又或者遊行示威見到CCTVB嘅採訪車，大家知道應該點做啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebabc92ca58af120ba5a104fc05b309b07ddaa0","tid":1300418,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:30:47.000Z","msg":"公正不偏報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kfboaEJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkfboaEJ.jpg&h=2d7562d5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}